集</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最早D有暗示應該係支離人(未生)<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSNTZU8NvZ8Zuea5qKxAsfdGr7QSoPsV3tsfvP1s2XSUY?filename=SiE0h.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSiE0h.gif&h=5cd1640c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWAnTsRt3QgnHUuB1E38niqmSuWFY2mtbEQhZFAdNbc9W?filename=N1Y61.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1Y61.gif&h=08fa447e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(合成)果陣已被綁架<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTVVLSiTv41vu8ydPe4xnDieMdrM6C6ZXq4kh9G9UhxKG?filename=3SP1o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3SP1o.gif&h=627f4c6a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw講多D最經典既(頭髮)如果資料時間無錯,<br />\n<br />\n應該都係參考佐&quot;雷爾運動&quot;既主張<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096ed0f2b060ea1f9adea5346ca08cf19f737690","tid":84101,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:06:42.000Z","msg":"成日話自己想快啲死真好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecac00157d703e010edd81fe698d3afdb50b09eb","tid":84101,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:11:54.000Z","msg":"後期衛斯理煩左好多  最後個d直頭悶<br />\n<br />\n但前期真係正到癲<br />\n<br />\n後期既思想儀系列唔錯 幾特別"},{"pid":"7967165f8edb752265963aa3d8bbfb27c8a9eacc","tid":84101,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>後期衛斯理煩左好多  最後個d直頭悶<br />\n<br />\n但前期真係正到癲<br />\n<br />\n後期既思想儀系列唔錯 幾特別</blockquote><br />\n衛斯理後期無咁深刻，但都唔差<br />\n早期就好睇d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a7770afbb895f9a3fc626fd64bbad0384ae85d","tid":84101,"uid":44948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:24:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大廈係第一本令我驚既書<br />\n搞到成個月搭lift都凝住凝住</blockquote><br />\n屌 same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大廈真係好正, 跟住嗰兩個月搭lift真係驚. Utube 有廣播劇版嘅衛斯理小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b379f4209d832f7f0cba307bcc6f22dbc796370c","tid":84101,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:38:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"662b776d2e5a3fe683f81201c845f647f4fee141","tid":84101,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:44:07.000Z","msg":"《中國超人》（英文：The Super Inframan）是1975年香港邵氏電影公司炮製的一部電影。由於日本於1970年代推出了一系列的《假面騎士》電視劇，紅遍了台灣、香港、韓國等亞洲地區，所以在《假面騎士》的潮流底下，推出了這部電影。該齣電影由蔡瀾作為製作經理，科幻小說家<span style=\"color: red;\">倪匡</span>編劇，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_JXBobRKYXEQ/SJf-1r-FRNI/AAAAAAAABA0/BXx5QiO_ibo/s400/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B6%85%E4%BA%BA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F_JXBobRKYXEQ%2FSJf-1r-FRNI%2FAAAAAAAABA0%2FBXx5QiO_ibo%2Fs400%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B6%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA.jpg&h=d84d9a03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"967829f068099bf1c72286a0cb34b532f5af3e9c","tid":84101,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i1109.photobucket.com/albums/h434/ppp98pp/Inframan/IFM2_zps86d7e642.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1109.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh434%2Fppp98pp%2FInframan%2FIFM2_zps86d7e642.jpg&h=ce88e531&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22e62b43ecfa260175721ddabed2d089b03360e2","tid":84101,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:00:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大廈係第一本令我驚既書<br />\n搞到成個月搭lift都凝住凝住</blockquote><br />\n屌 same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大廈真係好正, 跟住嗰兩個月搭lift真係驚. Utube 有廣播劇版嘅衛斯理小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\