i\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇完傷感得黎又無奈，完全道出香港嘅命運，但係我地都只能睇住佢沉淪。"},{"pid":"dfb28085e6d1c18b34174dc930d87679706ca493","tid":84101,"uid":64271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:22:24.000Z","msg":"以前好憎睇書,睇左衛斯理先開始鐘意睇書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3888ce2eec148fdb9fe5fc663bc55ae36f5194","tid":84101,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢咁敢言真係好撚難得<br />\n金庸都奶左共<br />\n唉</blockquote><br />\n金庸幾時死"},{"pid":"423f9b969ee9941fcea908c67104451b863f2e88","tid":84101,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:40:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢咁敢言真係好撚難得<br />\n金庸都奶左共<br />\n唉</blockquote><br />\n金庸幾時死</blockquote><br />\n金庸不嬲都親共架啦"},{"pid":"d5d80431525da7ab1e0856b8e3d3285c35e3caa5","tid":84101,"uid":4728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f481b4d621115d91c60415b964803f913a9dac4","tid":84101,"uid":34838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢咁敢言真係好撚難得<br />\n金庸都奶左共<br />\n唉</blockquote><br />\n倪匡親身經歷講土改，相比我睇任何關於土改嘅書都獲益良多<br />\n真係聽君一席話，勝讀十年書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b77084643c646ec3e8d4a986e4eecb13007d223","tid":84101,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:00:13.000Z","msg":"佢睇支那真係睇得好透<br />\nBtw<br />\n呢個post已經有人想轉移話題"},{"pid":"7721af426b9e3e9c40eb4aaad93ade9b0ae181aa","tid":84101,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>年輕人唔理上代人嘅經驗，一樣事事碰壁，發展得仲慢，佢講有另類意思的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：倪匡迷</blockquote><br />\n其實冇必要咁分<br />\n年輕人好多時都係引領新思潮<br />\n有時係進步<br />\n但都有退步既時候<br />\n例如法西斯，共產主義，hippies等<br />\n最緊要係討論既時候盡量避開幾個邏輯謬誤<br />\n因人廢言，估人動機，循環論證，打稻草人<br />\n基本上任何階層參與既討論都會有益</blockquote><br />\n法西斯<br />\n共產咪又係廢中引爆出來<br />\n咪屈年輕人"},{"pid":"e24342bc946dde442e28607ecd104445f55dbfa2","tid":84101,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"在數難逃講中共最多，睇完都好悲涼"},{"pid":"ebc0995b7004d74bb166adc379f57698342676b5","tid":84101,"uid":34838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:10:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>年輕人唔理上代人嘅經驗，一樣事事碰壁，發展得仲慢，佢講有另類意思的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：倪匡迷</blockquote><br />\n其實冇必要咁分<br />\n年輕人好多時都係引領新思潮<br />\n有時係進步<br />\n但都有退步既時候<br />\n例如法西斯，共產主義，hippies等<br />\n最緊要係討論既時候盡量避開幾個邏輯謬誤<br />\n因人廢言，估人動機，循環論證，打稻草人<br />\n基本上任何階層參與既討論都會有益</blockquote><br />\n法西斯<br />\n共產咪又係廢中引爆出來<br />\n咪屈年輕人</blockquote><br />\n共產主義同法西斯主義雖然唔係由青年人提出；但二十世紀嘅青少年至為推祟呢兩種極端主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0605b93c94f0a06340ff0b88c226c6b91d58d5a4","tid":84101,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:32:39.000Z","msg":"話說原振俠好唔好睇"},{"pid":"49c0eb3cbac7385f00cb9b883c73a50465875acf","tid":84101,"uid":34838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有智慧就唔會替耶教説話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢話過佢後生信佛教,但太多道理佢唔明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來發現基督教道理淺白,剩係需要信,啱哂佢呢d懶人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw我覺得佢講嘢似佛偈多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5227b5d70fa3103729b9ed04fa77b5f0c760d991","tid":84101,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:42:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有智慧就唔會替耶教説話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢話過佢後生信佛教,但太多道理佢唔明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來發現基督教道理淺白,剩係需要信,啱哂佢呢d懶人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw我覺得佢講嘢似佛偈多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有智慧先懶得理,兩袖清風<br />\n佢死過返生有咩睇唔透"},{"pid":"58de293487facc4d8608cbe5a9831b4325fd2b04","tid":84101,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:56:48.000Z","msg":"同19才子個段好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bbb40641c81805b7553115ff42947f3ca30d170","tid":84101,"uid":25516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:05:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇到烈火女<br />\n突然爆個女出嚟<br />\n之後無睇了<br />\n<br />\n但無可否認<br />\n前期故事好多好好睇</blockquote><br />\n女不嬲都有<br />\n最初提有個女係講隻猩猩同研究員人獸交嗰集</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最早D有暗示應該係支離人(未生)<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSNTZU8NvZ8Zuea5qKxAsfdGr7QSoPsV3tsfvP1s2XSUY?filename=SiE0h.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSiE0h.gif&h=5cd1640c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWAnTsRt3QgnHUuB1E38niqmSuWFY2mtbEQhZFAdNbc9W?filename=N1Y61.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1Y61.gif&h=08fa447e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(合成)果陣已被綁架<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTVVLSiTv41vu8ydPe4xnDieMdrM6C6ZXq4kh9G9UhxKG?filename=3SP1o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3SP1o.gif&h=627f4c6a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw講多D最經典既(頭髮)如果資料時間無錯,<br />\n<br />\n應該都係參考佐&quot;雷爾運動&quot;既主張<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有冇諗過佢係唔記得咗有個女，之後記起先再寫返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}